title: Camp Marmaduke
description: Team O'Neill surfers Jordy Smith, Cory Lopez, Timmy Reyes, Torrey Meister, Nate Yeomans, Ian Crane, Brett Barley and Soli Bailey recently took a trip to Western Australia to test out the latest O'Neill suits. They stayed at a house that had the name "Marmaduke House". The good vibes and strict, 4 surfs sessions a day, made it more like a camp. Therefore, we named our WA home "Camp Marmaduke". This video is the outcome. Enjoy!
